What if SMS verification fails?
    1. Apologize
    2. Tell user to leave username & phone number
    3. Tell user we'll call back immediately
    4. CMS -> Search Phone No. -> Info -> Verification Code

Do you have lawyers?
    We are a netural platform, so we recommend you to use your own lawyers.
    However, if you would like us to introduce some, we can.
    We do not take in commission.
